3414.Name: New Year's Resolution 2022 Women's PTI 40+ Tournament
3414.Details:
BPC is proud to present the New Year's Resolution 2022 Women's Tournament. Start the year by challenging yourself to play more (and better!) paddle.

To be eligible for this tournament, all players must have a PTI of 40 or higher.
Host site is BPC, but some matches will be played at neighboring clubs.
All back draw matches will play a 10-point super tiebreaker for the 3rd set. 
All Teams are guaranteed a minimum of 3 matches.

Draw will be limited to 16 teams but we will consider increasing the draw size based on demand.  
Please email the tournament director if the draw is full and you want to be on the wait list.

Tournament director is Brian Smith (brian@brooklinepaddle.com)

PLEASE REGISTER BY CLICKING ON LINK ABOVE
3414.RegistrationDetails:
Entry fee of $120 per team includes lunch, snacks, swag for all, prize for finalists.

Draw will be limited to 16 teams but we will consider increasing the draw size based on demand.  
Please email the tournament director if the draw is full and you want to be on the wait list.

Tournament director is Brian Smith (brian@booklinepaddle.com)
